OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine
OL,7,Fbut cloud along the East Lothian and
OL,8,FBerwickshire coast gradually edging
OL,9,Finland tonight, but the Southwest
OL,10,FBorders, and Dumfries and Galloway
OL,11,Fremaining clear, and turning quite
OL,12,Fchilly there.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FLow cloud in the east
OL,15,Fburning back to the coast, otherwise
OL,16,Fdry and sunny. Very warm or hot in the
OL,17,Fsouthwest, cooler in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
