OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand settled few days with variable
OL,7,Famounts of cloud and some sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Turning warmer in east, while
OL,9,Fthe west cools off a little.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
